extendedInfo.description: Song Squid Music Search will provide you with easy to access online resources for songs past and present.  Search using complete or partial song title or artist name, or even just a few words from the song.  An audio clip of the song automatically streams to your player if you don't already have the song on your device. SongSquid gives you direct access to streaming audio, song lyrics, biographies, discographies, news, tours, mp3 downloads, youtube and vevo videos, official web, myspace, and facebook pages, twitter streams, online radio stations, sheet music, midi files, guitar chords, and more! Assign audio as ringtones for individual contacts. This app is fully integrated with your mobile music library allowing you to discover more about any song on your device at the touch of a button or automatically as the song plays in the default Android Music Player, Winamp, and some other media players. Supports shared bookmarking so you can quickly return to your favorite tracks and access them with either Guitar Squid, Lyric Squid, MIDI Squid or Song Squid from any web browser.  If you want to upgrade your music listening experience or discover more about the music you love then this is the app for you!The free version is supported by Ads.  If you don't like ads then please purchase the pro version!PERMISSION EXPLANATION----------------------INTERNETRequired to access online servicesACCESS_NETWORK_STATERequired to provide warnings about bandwidth when not using WIFIREAD_PHONE_STATERequired to uniquely identify device and mute audio for incoming callsWRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGERequired to save mp3, lyrics, chords, and MIDI files to deviceWRITE_SETTINGSRequired to prevent screen turning off during photo slideshowSET_WALLPAPERRequired to set photo of artist as phone wallpaperREAD_CONTACTS and WRITE_CONTACTSRequired to set audio file as ringtone for individual contacts
